FBIS4-49248 "drchi086_u_94001" FBIS-CHI-94-086 Daily Report 3 May 1994 PRC MEDIA ON TAIWAN AFFAIRS ARATS Secretary General Zou Zhekai Leaves Office ARATS Secretary General Zou Zhekai Leaves Office HK0305123394 Beijing ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE in Chinese 1115 GMT 3 May 94 HK0305123394 Beijing ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE Chinese BFN [Report: "ARATS Confirms Secretary General Zou Zhekai Has Left Office"] [Text] Beijing, 3 May (ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE)--In a dispatch sent to Taiwan's Straits Exchange Foundation [SEF] today, the Association for Relations Across the Strait [ARATS] confirmed that ARATS Secretary General Zou Zhekai has already left office. In the dispatch to the SEF, ARATS stated: Mr. Zhekai Zou is no longer secretary general of ARATS. He now works in XINHUA Hong Kong Branch. Zou Zhekai asked us, ARATS, to relay his gratitude to all the gentlemen of the SEF for their support for his work during his term of office as ARATS secretary general.
